DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       This function can be used to disable certain (security) features in TLS
       in  order to maintain maximum compatibility with buggy clients. Because
       several trade-offs with security are enabled, if required they will  be
       reported through the audit subsystem.

       Normally  only  servers  that require maximum compatibility with every-
       thing out there, need to call this function.

       Note that this function must be called after any call to  gnutls_prior-
       ity functions.

